{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act22side", "eventName": "照我以火", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "FC-3", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "引燃草垛", "storyInfo": "在隊伍的去向上，葦草與塞爾蒙產生了分歧。從一開始，塞爾蒙就不是逃難的流民，她想和深池一樣，解救更多塔拉人。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_manorindoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歷史記載中，最後的蓋爾王有感於德拉克與阿斯蘭之間持久的戰爭太過慘烈，於是簽下了和平協議。", "name": "衣著樸素的詩人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傳說他選擇了銷熔戰士的兵器以示決心，而他的臣子難以接受這樣的失敗，因此合謀造反，刺殺了這位君主。", "name": "衣著樸素的詩人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但正如您在多次演講中所說，一場刺殺不足以滅亡一整支紅龍的血脈。", "name": "衣著樸素的詩人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_727_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞人無論如何書寫史書，都無法改變我們親眼所見的事實。", "name": "沃里克伯爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_727_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿斯蘭曾經許諾與德拉克分享維多利亞的王位，近百年來卻不曾交出那頂冠冕。", "name": "沃里克伯爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_727_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然獅子們的野心已經昭彰至此，當初刺死蓋爾王的六處劍痕，我想，也多少出自阿斯蘭之手。", "name": "沃里克伯爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_727_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更何況自那以後，德拉克逃出王城，不知所終。而失去統治者的塔拉王國，似乎順理成章地被納入維多利亞君主的權柄之下。", "name": "沃里克伯爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_727_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阻止德拉克返回王城的，想必也不是他自己的臣民。", "name": "沃里克伯爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_727_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_727_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因此，我很欣賞你基於塔拉人自己的歌謠寫成的劇作，你領著人們看到了更多歷史的真相。", "name": "沃里克伯爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_727_1#8$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_239"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多謝您的賞識。", "name": "衣著樸素的詩人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為寫作這個故事，我在鄉野間看過一些戲劇，也拜訪過幾位繼承了塔拉傳統的吟遊詩人。", "name": "衣著樸素的詩人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——只是，我看得最多的不是塔拉文化的垂危，而是許多生命正在消逝。", "name": "衣著樸素的詩人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您或許認為，要先有塔拉人的理想國，與維多利亞劃清界限，塔拉人才能得救。", "name": "衣著樸素的詩人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我想，如果我們自身能過上更好的生活，如果為那許多不識字的塔拉人埋下思想的種子......", "name": "衣著樸素的詩人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們是否就已經戰勝了想讓我們一生困於貧窮無知的維多利亞人？", "name": "衣著樸素的詩人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_239"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g3_swamp_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帶著那些人一起走？想都別想。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在你要等他們休息，要把自己的食物分給他們，我還能接受。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但那是我們這兩天運氣好躲過了巡邏隊，要是下次沒躲過呢？那些七八歲的小孩，又不能拿起武器反抗，又跑不快，你要怎麼辦？", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以戰鬥......我會保護他們。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們想穿過無人區，徹底逃離特倫特郡控制的區域，這一路，我都可以協助你們。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "透過風笛和陳......我的同事們幫忙，我聯繫到了我所屬的企業，確認了最近的安全屋，恰好在這個方向上。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是幾頂帳篷和少量野外應急物資的話，他們能順利轉運過來。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也知道，那邊......是一位好心的公爵的領地。到了那裡，至少，你們不會再被軍隊追捕。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的？真有什麼貴族老爺對我們這樣的人是好心的？", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他有......庇護塔拉人的理由。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼知道？", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......也許很快，所有人都會知道了。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帶上那些人，我們也有辦法生存下去。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，你別忘了，他們是感染者啊。", "name": "緊張的塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們是逃命逃出來的，幹嘛還要把死亡招到自己身邊？", "name": "緊張的塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且得了病的人，也不知道什麼時候就會發作，哪一次就徹底斷氣了......", "name": "緊張的塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你救這種人，有什麼意義？", "name": "緊張的塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只知道，當時有人救了我......我也想問她，為什麼？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明明......我就快死了。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這是什麼意思？", "name": "緊張的塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也是感染者。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#4$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？啊，呃......", "name": "緊張的塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳，好吧，其實感染者也沒什麼。要是沒有你幫忙，我們也不見得能比感染者活得久，哈哈。", "name": "緊張的塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過......", "name": "緊張的塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是站在一起，是不會傳染礦石病的。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，你害怕的話，可以離遠一些，我不在乎。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，帶上那些感染者一起逃吧......相信我。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哎，我信你！塞爾蒙，你也聽她一句勸告吧......", "name": "緊張的塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——我不逃。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要帶上那些不能打架的人，那就帶吧，隨便你好了。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我的目的絕對不會變。我要回到深池。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_offce", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241", "name2": "avg_npc_248", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......那兩支部隊已經失蹤一周了，可以推測，這種與曾經鬼魂部隊相關事件類似的情形，與深池有關。", "name": "嚴肅的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241", "name2": "avg_npc_248", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "類似？不，我們眼下面對的情況完全不同。", "name": "尖刻的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前這些叛亂者只是糾集起來的一支武裝力量，出現在某一處，發動襲擊，僅此而已。", "name": "尖刻的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，疑似深池引發的暴力事件在整個維多利亞南部各處發生。", "name": "尖刻的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241", "name2": "avg_npc_248", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......特倫特侯爵還堅持他的命令嗎？", "name": "嚴肅的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241", "name2": "avg_npc_248", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。無論移動城市外報上來了多少可疑情況，我們都必須一一厘清，把這一地區的局勢控制住。", "name": "尖刻的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241", "name2": "avg_npc_248", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，在各種小型衝突裡，真正可疑的似乎只有紅脊鎮的縱火事件，而且那次火情也沒有後續。", "name": "嚴肅的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許我們該把這一部分卷宗暫時挪走？還是留下？", "name": "嚴肅的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請把上述卷宗借給我吧，長官們。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是......開......", "name": "嚴肅的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "打招呼的部分還請省略。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以及，和過去一樣，不必將此次卷宗調閱記錄在案。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次縱火事件......或許值得開展一次深入調查。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_forest", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喝口水吧，布蘭登老爺子，我還撿了點漿果。這地方有這麼深的樹林，應該離聚落也不遠了。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小荷莉，你也要吃？那吃過之後，下午的路就自己走，不要讓人抱你了，好不好？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你呢，莫蘭？不對，我記得你不吃這麼甜的......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......謝謝您。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......唉。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242", "name2": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，我們要在這裡停留多久？", "name": "暴躁的塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242", "name2": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風笛和陳去幫我們取東西啦。正好大家都走累了，可以休息一會。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別擔心，敲熄火鐘之前我們肯定能到最近的聚落。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡離我們鬧出事的地方也夠遠了，要是留在這裡，躲起來過日子，應該不會被抓住。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242", "name2": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行，漿果也給我抓一把。這麼多天了，難得看到你開心的樣子。", "name": "暴躁的塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242", "name2": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，有嗎？我只是覺得葦草挺可靠的，她那兩個朋友也是，又能打，又是好心人。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242", "name2": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的？難道不是因為你的苦日子也要到頭了？", "name": "暴躁的塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們要繼續往荒地上走，去找深池部隊，加入他們。你呢，肯定更願意在聚落留下來吧。", "name": "暴躁的塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242", "name2": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......呃，也不一定吧。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242", "name2": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......唉，我還是不喜歡你們這麼幹。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一開始沒遇到塞爾蒙的時候，明明我們想的都是逃就行了，逃得越遠越好。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後來不順心的事越來越多，你們才一個個地被她說動了，想加入深池。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242", "name2": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們......都沒遇見過真的深池部隊吧？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g3_swamp_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還在想葦草的事情？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她之前借我們的通信裝置，當著我們的面聯繫了羅德島。取物資的事情也很順利。種種跡象表明，她不像是騙了我們。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，倒不是說懷疑啦，我只是有點擔心......她真的恢復過來了嗎？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算是瓦伊凡，她的生命力也讓我覺得有點吃驚......一開始我們沒認出對方的時候，她揮過來的那一下，把我手都震疼了。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過這也算是好事吧，我只是總覺得，她還有很多心事。明明是她自己想做的事情，她卻顯得很痛苦。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有什麼？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#6$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的戰鬥方式總讓我覺得有些熟悉。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時在小丘郡，Outcast把她帶回來之前，我是不是就見過她？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shallowswalk", "volume": 0.7, "loop": "true", "channel": "walksp"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "walksp", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎哎，葦草你來啦！正好，我和陳陳正在說......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我們在說接下來該往哪裡走。這條路剛好能通往最近的聚落。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，這個方向，不能再走了......我去告訴其他人，停下來。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "風笛", "content": "你是說......"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "風笛", "end": "true", "content": "陳陳，九點鐘方向！", "joined": "你是說......陳陳，九點鐘方向！"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_metallicclick", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.1}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_slash_02_l", "y": 80.0, "roy": 80.0, "roz": 90.0, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_metalcollar", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_metalcollar", "volume": 0.2, "loop": "false", "channel": "cutdown", "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隱在灌木叢間的騎兵刀斷作兩截。"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "握著那把刀的人並沒有動彈。陳確定自己剛才的那一劍並沒有傷到人，可是草叢間有鮮血灑出的痕跡。深色的，已經乾涸的血。"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死者是......巡邏隊的人？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，是駐軍。那邊還有更多。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弩箭，刀劍......還有法術的痕跡。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰鬥應該發生在一周之前。這支駐軍遭遇了埋伏，全軍覆沒。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#7$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那他們的敵人呢？為什麼連一具屍體都沒有留下？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們......已經離開了。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "全都離開了？可是戰鬥明明這麼激烈，雙方的損傷應該不相上下吧？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風笛，你還記得我們在遇見葦草之前發現的那群士兵嗎？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......那群中了奇怪法術，眼睛裡冒著火的......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草，你當時也在小丘郡，是不是同樣見過類似的士兵？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯，我知道他們。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們是......亡魂。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明明死去了，卻無法安息的可憐人......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道說，殺死這隊駐軍的人也都死了，並且在死後還在行軍？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們之前追蹤到的交火痕跡，也是相似的情況。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......只有這一種可能性。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#7$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陳陳，我不知道你怎麼想，可是我......不太能接受這樣的事。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼樣的人，會在別人死後，還要繼續控制他們？這也太殘忍了。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hidehaystack"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......塞爾蒙？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們才沒有死去。你們全都猜錯了。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我們都親眼見到了......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們看到的都是其他地方發生的事。我只相信自己看到的。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深池戰勝了維多利亞的部隊。他們贏了，去了下一個地方，正準備解救更多塔拉人。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一定要......", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你在擔心什麼嗎？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別裝得像是我的老大一樣。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維恩他們願意跟著你，隨他們的便。我知道你跟我們不是一路人，你跟那兩個瓦伊凡才是一起的。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#7$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你只想把我們安置起來，確保我們不會在今天死掉，讓我們去過那種被維多利亞安排好了的、看不見明天的生活。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到了那時候，你就會把我們拋下。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說錯了嗎，“領袖”？", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不要這樣叫我......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，“不”，這是我從你這裡聽到最多遍的詞語。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在我要走了，就從你不想讓我們走的這條路走。不就是戰場和死亡嗎？塔拉人哪一樣見得少了？", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我再也不想聽見什麼外人來對我們說“不”。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shallowswalk", "volume": 0.7, "loop": "true", "channel": "walksp1"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "walksp1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她很生氣，但真正惹她生氣的人不是你。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你......呃，你還好嗎？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想跟著她。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰場上......可能會留下還沒有引爆的地雷，還有殘留的法術。就這樣走過去的話，會有危險。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們能幫我叫上其他人嗎？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你本想讓那些塔拉人繞開戰場。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，塞爾蒙說，這是他們的選擇。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我......我承諾過，會護送他們，直到......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到我不再被需要為止。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}